Working Here

STAY CONNECTED Join the Eldorado Resorts Talent Community today and become a member of our TEAM!

Connect With Us
Working Here
The Eldorado Resorts TEAM works together to make a difference every day for our guests and each other.We, as a top five regional gaming company in the industry, are only as extraordinary as our people. We’re lucky that way because business isn’t just about having the best games, restaurants or entertainment. It’s about our Team Members!
Each person plays a very important role in our success—making a difference in people’s lives. We go that extra mile for our guests because we know we can and we know it’s going to put a smile on their faces. We are committed to providing our guests with exceptional service so that they feel as if they are “home”when they are visiting any of our nineteen properties throughout the US. We are looking for candidates to join our team of passionate and energetic professionals who will share this commitment with us.
We invite you to take a look at the various Employment Opportunities at Eldorado Resorts and discover where you would be a great fit. Be sure to also join our Talent Community so we can keep in touch throughout your employment search.
Administrative Support
Discover opportunities to support our first class resorts in Finance, Human Resources, Internal Audit, Marketing, and many more.


  Finance   Financial management is critical to any organization. Eldorado Resorts offers a solid career opportunity for recent graduates, seasoned professionals, and everyone in-between. Examples of our career opportunities in Finance include:

 Financial and Operational Controllers
 Accountants
 Revenue Auditors
 Internal Auditors
 Vault and Retail Cashiers
 Purchasing Agents
 Warehouse Product Handlers
  
  Human Resources   Help us develop Eldorado Resorts into the employer of choice wherever we are located. We offer support to our Team Members with the following examples in Human Resources:

 Compensation and Benefits Analysts
 HR Generalists
 Trainers
 Event Coordinators
  
  Marketing   Our Team Members in Marketing establish the platform to communicate all of Eldorado’s excitement to our guests. Become part of the team that develops the media which encourages guests to visit our properties, or one that entertains them during their visit. Examples of careers in Marketing include:

 Tele-promotions
 Slot Promotions and Direct Mail Marketing
 Digital and Social Media Marketing Representatives
 Casino Hosts
 Player Development Representatives
  


Resort Operations
Become part of our Resort Operations Team at a variety of resorts throughout the US and provide best in class service at our Hotel’s Front Desk, Concierge/VIP Service, Reservations, Spa, Gift Shop, and other resort services.


  Hotel Management    Expand your guest service career in management at one of our properties. Our legendary family style of leadership makes guests feel at home in any one of these Hotel Management Examples:

Director of Resort Operations
Front Desk Manager
Transportation Manager
Housekeeping Manager
Gift Shop Supervisor
Golf Course Manager
  
  Front of the House   Your smile will brighten a guest’s day as you become the face of our company. The guest service skills you possess and will continually develop are necessary in these Front of the House examples:

 Front Desk Agent
 VIP Services Representative
 Spa Attendant
 Call Center Representative
 Security Officer

  
  Heart of the House    Teamwork is essential as you work to support the front line guest service operations. It takes everyone to exceed our guests’ expectations when visiting one of our properties. Examples of these support positions include:

 Housekeeper
 Maintenance Technician
 Information Technology Administrator
 Grounds Maintenance
 Stewart
 Surveillance Operator

  


Gaming
Exciting surroundings combined with state-of-the-art technology on our casino floors, where gaming takes center stage. Team Members work together to create a memorable gaming experience for our guests.


  Table Gaming and Slot Management   Learn to manage the excitement created by our Team Members and guests on the casino floor. You will have the opportunity to mentor and lead a team to deliver excitement in these position examples:

 Director of Gaming Operations
 Pit Manager
 Floor Supervisor
 Casino Shift Manager

  
  Casino Operations    Let your personality shine as you will have the opportunity to interact with multiple guests at extended intervals throughout your shift. You will directly contribute to delivering the Eldorado Resorts guest satisfaction in any one of these positions:

 Table Games Dealer
 Poker Dealer
 Craps Dealer
 Keno

  
  Slot Operations   The slot department will offer you the pleasure of getting to know players by their first name. They will become part of the Eldorado Resorts family as you make them feel at home in any of these Slot Department opportunities:

 Slot Service Representative
 Slot Technician

  


Racing
Several of our properties offer the excitement of live and simulcast Thoroughbred and Harness Horse Racing. Opportunities include Mutuel Tellers, Racing Administration, Simulcasting, Track Maintenance and Starting Gate, along with other jobs unique to our racing product.


  Mutuels   Talk about excitement. Imagine the joy and excitement you get to share with the guests as they wager on live horseracing. Your outgoing personality is a perfect fit for any of these wagering careers:

 Mutuel Teller – Live and Simulcast Racing
 Mutuel Money Room Attendant
  
  Racing Administration and Track Maintenance   Your teamwork skills will be at the forefront when you assist in the production of Eldorado’s racing product. Managing and coordinating each event will offer you the ability to demonstrate your organizational skills in these positions:

 Racing Secretary
 Placing Judge
 Video Technician
 Jocks Room Attendant
 Admissions Clerk
 Starting Gate Attendant
 Track Maintenance Crew Member
 Print Shop Technician
  


Food & Beverage
Eldorado Resorts offers the finest dining experiences, from our award winning Chefs at LBV Steakhouse, La Strada, Sterling’s Seafood Steakhouse, Roxy, and The Vintage, to our Famous Eldorado Buffet and 24 hour coffee shops. Imagine working in a unique venue such as Brew Brothers that features an on-site microbrewery, creative dining menu and one-of-a-kind entertainment in Nevada or Ohio! We offer careers in Culinary, Catering, Stewarding, Bar and Restaurant Management that will be sure to provide a rewarding employment experience:


  Restaurant Management    If you are looking to assist in creating a truly exceptional dining experience, then Eldorado Resorts has opportunities for you. Our dining experience is second to none and your restaurant management skills will demonstrate leadership, cooperation, and team work in these F&B Management examples:

 Director of F&B
 Beverage Manager
 Outlet Manager
 Shift Supervisor
  
  Culinary   Your career gets an immediate boost when you join our legendary Eldorado Resorts Culinary team. Bring your culinary talent and expertise to our award winning team in these positions:

 Executive Chef
 Assistant Chef
 Sous Chef
 Cook
 F&B Attendant
  
  Beverage   The Eldorado Resorts experience is all about feeling welcome, and the beverage team is essential in delivering exceptional service. Your guest service talent will be cultivated and showcased in these examples:

 Bartender
 Cocktail Server
 Bar-back
  


   

 




















