 Barista/Fountain Attendant-Circus Circus


 Eldorado Resort Casino- Reno, NV


Description:
 GENERAL SUMMARY OF DUTIES: Responsible for the ultimate professional guest service.  Knowledge of product, specialty items and cashiering. Cleanliness of the entire restaurant.
EXAMPLES OF DUTIES/ESSENTIAL FUNCTIONS: (Includes, but is not limited to the following)

Take daily orders, assist with stocking and guest requests.
Keep coffee shuttles full in amounts in accordance with guest volume.
Always work as a team player.
Keep tables, floor and chairs clean and clear of trash at all times.
Maintain side stations and cleanliness of restaurant.
Completion of side work and maintaining pars on all supplies.
Assist guests in a friendly, professional manner.
Utilize proper procedures and documentation for transactions.
Ensure bank is counted and balanced with cage.
Complete cash turn-in sheets, etc., and distribute accordingly.
Follow directions from Manager at all times.
Maintain proper uniform, ID badge and nametag at all times.
Maintain regular, predictable attendance.
Other job related duties as assigned.



Requirements:
 PERFORMANCE REQUIREMENTS: (Knowledge, Skills and Abilities) Understand and comply with all company and departmental rules and regulations, policies and procedures.  Skill in establishing and maintaining effective working relationships with staff and guests.  Ability to read, write and communicate verbally in English. 
EDUCATION AND EXPERIENCE:

Education: High school education or equivalent preferred.
Experience: Previous experience preferred, but will train.
Certificate/License: Must have permit to work in the U.S.








