			Company Description 


			Eldorado Resorts, Inc. is a gaming and hospitality company. The firm owns and operates gaming facilities located in Ohio, Louisiana, Nevada, Pennsylvania and West Virginia. It operates through the following geographic segments: Nevada, Louisiana, and Eastern parts of U.S. The company was founded in ...
		


                Eldorado Resorts, Inc. is a gaming and hospitality company. The firm owns and operates gaming facilities located in Ohio, Louisiana, Nevada, Pennsylvania and West Virginia. It operates through the following geographic segments: Nevada, Louisiana, and Eastern parts of U.S. The company was founded in 1973 and is headquartered in Reno, NV. .
            




